        "EXTERNAL INPAINT STEP (not included \u2014 needs Acly/comfyui-inpaint-nodes, GPL-3.0):\n\nThe links feeding the BG and MID AtlasCleanPlateLayer plate_image inputs are PLACEHOLDERS \u2014 they reuse OCIORead's sRGB-Display preview directly so this graph stays valid/runnable without the external pack installed.\n\nFor each of the two occluded bands, replace that link with:\n  AtlasDepthLayerMask.occlusion_mask\n    -> INPAINT_ExpandMask (grow ~16-32)\n    -> INPAINT_InpaintWithModel (image = OCIORead's image output, inpaint_model = INPAINT_LoadInpaintModel loading big-lama.pt)\n    -> AtlasCleanPlateLayer.plate_image\n\nThe FG layer needs no inpainting \u2014 it is wired to the original photo by design, since nothing occludes the frontmost band.\n\nEach AtlasCleanPlateLayer also exposes its own optional plate_ref (ATLAS_PLATE_REF) input, left unconnected here \u2014 wire an AtlasRegisterPlate per band if a real per-layer float clean plate ever exists (e.g. a separately rendered background pass); it is independent of the solve-level source_plate this workflow demonstrates."
      ]
    },
